Class AbstractLabels

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.NativeObjectContainer

          • org.pepstock.charba.client.treemap.AbstractLabels
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Captions, Labels
    abstract class AbstractLabels
extends AbstractDatasetNode
    Base class for inner nodes of TreeMapDataset which are representing a label on the chart, like Labels and Captions.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero

      • AbstractLabels

        AbstractLabels​(AbstractNode parent,
               Key childKey,
               IsDefaultOptions defaultValues,
               NativeObject nativeObject,
               boolean defaultDisplay)
        Creates the object with the parent, the key of this element, default values and native object to map java script properties.
        Parameters:
        parent - parent node to use to add this element where changed
        childKey - the property name of this element to use to add it to the parent.
        defaultValues - default options of the controller
        nativeObject - native object to map java script properties
        defaultDisplay - default value of display option. This can be different among inner nodes
